snippet.title: Longplay of Easter Bunny's Big Day
snippet.description:
Longplay of Easter Bunny's Big Day, played  as the NTSC version on the PlayStation. This game's version was released on Apr. 1st, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
01:40 - Candy Store
09:14 - Toy Shop
18:21 - Green Grocer
31:52 - Flower Shop
36:27 - Credits

By: Val
